            li High-power relay outputs for AC device control
            li Precise timing control for synchronized operations
            li Safety protection features for reliable operation
            li Web-based configuration for easy setup and management
            li Real-time status monitoring and diagnostics
            li Comprehensive web interface for configuration
            li DDP, Artnet, E1.31 & sACN compatible
            li High refresh rates for responsive control
            li Multiple relay outputs for distributed control
            li Small footprint compatible with standard mounting solutions

