            li AC lighting control and traditional lighting displays
            li Motor control applications and automation
            li Industrial automation and control systems
            li Safety-critical systems and applications
            li High-voltage switching and control
            li Commercial lighting installations
            li Industrial control applications
            li Safety-focused automation projects

